-- Amplifon to Pay $441 Million to Buy Australian Hearing Aid Company NHC
-- B y   J e r r o l d   C o l t e n
-- 2010-09-28T06:01:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/amplifon-to-pay-441-million-to-buy-australian-hearing-aid-company-nhc.html
Amplifon SpA said in a statement
today that it agreed to pay 460 million Australian dollars for
National Hearing Care.  NHC is a distributor of hearing care solutions with a
network of about 200 shops in Australia, New Zealand and India,
Amplifon said in the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jerrold Colten at 
 jcolten@bloomberg.net  